{"tid":2302174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄指不參與內地考察會否影響校內成績由學校決定","createTime":"2020-11-27T02:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T08:49:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":176,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"7e367977345a023079ad3347cffe52d55d8ad863","tid":2302174,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:22:56.000Z","msg":"新高中課程通識科將會改革，公開試只分合格或不合格，亦加入到內地考察活動。教育局局長楊潤雄說，不會迫學生到內地，但希望給予機會讓學生增廣見聞，對考察項目有更深入的了解，至於推行細節要交由課程發展議會考慮。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，考察不會計入公開試分數，至於學生如果不參與會否影響校內成績，就由學校決定。<br />\n<br />\n被問到部分中學生曾參與社會運動，到內地考察是否需要預先審查，楊潤雄表示，學校可按實際情況與教育局商量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562281-20201127.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562281-20201127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=c6502a9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562281-20201127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=878e2784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562281-20201127.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c8cc5ac5bbea3927e774b624dabc852bbc934531","tid":2302174,"uid":152476,"like":76,"dislike":2,"score":74,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:24:02.000Z","msg":"拋個波俾學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa18f5f29f7f13544ea0406d053dac3de864da7d","tid":2302174,"uid":22609,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"c8cc5ac5bbea3927e774b624dabc852bbc934531","tid":2302174,"uid":152476,"like":76,"dislike":2,"score":74,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:24:02.000Z","msg":"拋個波俾學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:25:12.000Z","msg":"邊間學校唔影響成績就清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c549f4b05424809e56ebf0d8f2cf99fc7a5d83ef","tid":2302174,"uid":33099,"l